{
  "info": {
    "name": "Calls & SIP Integration API",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the unified Calls & SIP Integration API with 9 endpoints covering inbound webhook, SIP events, manual logging, listing, stats, phone lookup, updates, and backward-compatible telephony endpoints.\n\n## Authentication\n- **Inbound webhook**: HMAC-SHA256 via `X-Webhook-Signature` header (auto-generated in pre-request scripts)\n- **All other endpoints**: JWT Bearer token via `Authorization` header (auto-set via Login request)\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `{{baseUrl}}` — Server base URL (default: http://localhost:5000)\n- `{{webhookSecret}}` — HMAC signing key for inbound webhook\n- `{{authToken}}` — Auto-populated JWT from Login request\n\n## Getting Started\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set `{{webhookSecret}}` in collection variables to match your `TELEPHONY_WEBHOOK_SECRET`\n3. Run the \"Auth → Login\" request to auto-populate the JWT token\n4. Start testing the webhook, SIP, and call management endpoints",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookSecret",
      "value": "a3f8c1e9d4b7a2f6c9e8b1d5f7a3c6e9b2d4f8a1c5e7b9d3f6a8c1e9f2a59f2a5"
    },
    {
      "key": "authToken",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{authToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (get JWT token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved:', jsonData.data.token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@medilead.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Inbound Webhook (HMAC-SHA256)",
      "description": "POST /api/calls/inbound — Telephony vendor webhook. All requests auto-generate HMAC-SHA256 signature via pre-request script.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Completed Call — Intercom 1001",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var body = pm.request.body.raw;",
                  "var secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('webhookSecret');",
                  "var sig = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();",
                  "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-Webhook-Signature', value: sig });",
                  "console.log('HMAC Signature:', sig);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"caller_phone_number\": \"+919876543210\",\n  \"call_status\": \"completed\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-24T10:45:00Z\",\n  \"duration_seconds\": 142,\n  \"vendor_call_id\": \"vc_completed_001\",\n  \"direction\": \"inbound\",\n  \"intercom_number\": \"1001\",\n  \"recording_url\": \"https://recordings.example.com/calls/vc_completed_001.mp3\"\n}"
